description: Lists the AI Prompts available on the Amazon Q in Connect assistant.

parameters.name: assistantId
parameters.description: The identifier of the Amazon Q in Connect assistant. Can be either the ID or the ARN. URLs cannot contain the ARN.

nested_items.name: aiPromptSummaries
nested_items.description: The summaries of the AI Prompts.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the AI Prompt.

nested_items.name: assistantId
nested_items.description: The identifier of the Amazon Q in Connect assistant. Can be either the ID or the ARN. URLs cannot contain the ARN.

nested_items.name: assistantArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Amazon Q in Connect assistant.

nested_items.name: aiPromptId
nested_items.description: The identifier of the Amazon Q in Connect AI prompt.

nested_items.name: type
nested_items.description: The type of this AI Prompt.

nested_items.name: aiPromptArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the AI Prompt.

nested_items.name: modifiedTime
nested_items.description: The time the AI Prompt was last modified.

nested_items.name: templateType
nested_items.description: The type of the prompt template for this AI Prompt.

nested_items.name: modelId
nested_items.description: The identifier of the model used for this AI Prompt. Model Ids supported are: anthropic.claude-3-haiku-20240307-v1:0.

nested_items.name: apiFormat
nested_items.description: The API format used for this AI Prompt.

nested_items.name: visibilityStatus
nested_items.description: The visibility status of the AI Prompt.

nested_items.name: origin
nested_items.description: The origin of the AI Prompt. SYSTEM for a default AI Prompt created by Q in Connect or CUSTOMER for an AI Prompt created by calling AI Prompt creation APIs.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: The description of the AI Prompt.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the AI Prompt.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The token for the next set of results. Use the value returned in the previous response in the next request to retrieve the next set of results.
